			"content_html": "<p>“For Trump to pardon him [is] an assault on the federal judiciary, the Constitution and the rule of law itself. … it [is] an impeachable offense” —<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/view/articles/2017-08-23/arpaio-pardon-would-show-contempt-for-constitution\">Noah Feldman</a></p>\n",
			"date_published": "2017-08-26T15:47:00-07:00",
			"url": "http://microblog.curtclifton.net/2017/08/26/for-trump-to.html"
		},
		
		{
			"id": "http://curt.micro.blog/2017/08/26/one-day-trump.html",
	      	
			"content_html": "<p>“One day, Trump will do something really awful. And on that day, I will also draft a very stern letter, which I will place into a drawer and not send.” —<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/compost/wp/2017/08/25/my-letter-of-not-quite-resignation-from-the-trump-white-house/\">Alexandra Petri, channeling Gary Cohn</a></p>\n",
			"date_published": "2017-08-26T13:02:00-07:00",
			"url": "http://microblog.curtclifton.net/2017/08/26/one-day-trump.html"
		},
		
		{
